NOTICE OF MOTION

DEFENDANT GHISLAINE MAXWELL'S NOTICE OF MOTION
TO STRIKE SURPLUSAGE FROM SUPERSEDING INDICTMENT
(Pretrial Motion # 6)

PLEASE TAKE NOTICE that, upon the accompanying memorandum of law, Defendant Ghislaine Maxwell, through counsel, hereby moves to strike surplusage from the superseding indictment.

New York, New York
